# Deploy Rules

Flow: code on SG-Lab → verify on SG-Lab → push to Gitee → Linus deploys to SG-Dev → Knuth verifies (2026-03-28)
Never push untested code to Gitee | SG-Lab is the first testing ground (2026-03-28)
develop is the source of truth branch | deploy/v2-code is stale, don't use it (2026-03-28)
Knuth must verify every deploy before reporting done | premature "done" reports erode trust (2026-03-28)
Linus is deploy gatekeeper | coders push code, Linus handles builds and deploys (2026-03-28)
Backend first, frontend second on SG-Dev | frontend may reference new API endpoints that don't exist yet (2026-03-28)
Login endpoint accepts form-encoded POST only, not JSON | Spring Security formLogin bug — JSON returns fake "Account locked" error (2026-03-28)
